uilderFactory behavior.\\n\\nNew uncovered feature added:\\n- `RestClientSsl` auto-configured SSL bundle support for `RestClient.Builder`.\\n\\nAdded test:\\n- `restClientSslAppliesNamedSslBundleToRestClientRequestFactory`\\n  - Registers a named `SslBundle` via `DefaultSslBundleRegistry`.\\n  - Obtains the public `RestClientSsl` bean from `RestClientAutoConfiguration`.\\n  - Applies the named bundle to a `RestClient.Builder`.\\n  - Verifies the configured request factory builder receives the selected `SslBundle`.\\n  - Performs an actual bounded local HTTP request through the resulting `RestClient` to confirm the customized builder remains functional.\\n\\nNo reachability metadata or build files were modified. Tests were not run, per instruction.\", \"textSignature\": \"{\\\"v\\\":1,\\\"id\\\":\\\"msg_026609c108a895f2016a0c990df8948196913e684677af1730\\\",\\\"phase\\\":\\\"final_answer\\\"}\"}], \"api\": \"openai-responses\", \"provider\": \"OCA\", \"model\": \"gpt-5.5\", \"usage\": {\"input\": 1007, \"output\": 492, \"cacheRead\": 33280, \"cacheWrite\": 0, \"totalTokens\": 34779, \"cost\": {\"input\": 0, \"output\": 0, \"cacheRead\": 0, \"cacheWrite\": 0, \"total\": 0}}, \"stopReason\": \"stop\", \"timestamp\": 1779210506293, \"responseId\": \"resp_026609c108a895f2016a0c990abfa8819699720b2eba7cd5b2\"}, \"toolResults\": []}\n[recv] agent_end\n[send] get_state\n[recv] get_state success\n  sessionFile: ../../../../../../../../.pi/agent/sessions/--home-vjovanov-c-forge-forge2-graalvm-reachability-metadata-forge-local_repositories-forge_worktrees-7071-f36ff061--/2026-05-19T17-06-49-024Z_019e4134-5440-74e9-820e-9d876f6e0613.jsonl\n  sessionId: 019e4134-5440-74e9-820e-9d876f6e0613\n[send] get_session_stats\n[recv] get_session_stats success\n  tokens: input=36293 output=6198 cacheRead=408064 cacheWrite=0 total=450555\n\n","exit_code":0,"status":"completed"}}
